00:25:47,200 --> 00:25:49,899
<i>[Manager]</i>

311
00:25:51,899 --> 00:25:54,599
I told you that I'm
taking the day off today!

312
00:25:54,599 --> 00:25:57,399
<i>Hey, where are you right now?</i>

313
00:25:58,800 --> 00:26:04,399
Man, staying in my room this whole time
sure makes me feel cramped!

314
00:26:10,300 --> 00:26:13,899
Just where did this guy go, though?

315
00:26:17,599 --> 00:26:20,000
Why are you peeking
