to go through something like this again?

373
00:30:33,000 --> 00:30:36,500
Hey, why are you acting like this,
all of a sudden?

374
00:30:36,500 --> 00:30:39,200
- Find another way.
- Another... way?

375
00:30:39,200 --> 00:30:42,800
