395
00:32:00,099 --> 00:32:03,200
Hey, what are you doing?

396
00:32:04,000 --> 00:32:06,000
Ta-da!

397
00:32:07,399 --> 00:32:11,200
Hey, why did you buy so much?

398
00:32:11,200 --> 00:32:13,800
You feel totally thankful, right?

399
00:32:13,800 --> 00:32:15,899
I even cut them for you, like this

400
00:32:15,899 --> 00:32:19,800
