they'd re-stitch them for me!

403
00:32:26,800 --> 00:32:30,009
What does it matter if you cut it there?

404
00:32:30,009 --> 00:32:32,000
I'm sure that my thighs
won't even fit into those!

405
00:32:32,000 --> 00:32:34,700
Don't worry. I knew
you'd say that, and...

406
00:32:35,800 --> 00:32:39,099
You see this? I even bought you a dress.

407
00:32:39,099 --> 00:32:43,599
At any rate, I'll fill up your closet
for you, so wear these clothes.

408
00:32:43,599 --> 00:32:44,599
Got it?

409
00:32:45,200 --> 00:32:47,000
Geez, you...

410
00:32:47,000 --> 00:32:49,800
What? Want me to put
these clothes on you, too?

411
00:32:49,800 --> 00:32:51,399
- Sure, if you want--
- Wait!

412
00:32:51,399 --> 00:32:53,000
That's enough.

413
00:32:54,300 --> 00:32:56,599
- Thanks.
- Okay.

414
00:32:57,399 --> 00:32:59,500
- Thanks!
- Sure!

415
00:33:05,000 --> 00:33:06,800
Chairman.

416
00:33:07,300 --> 00:33:11,099
