438
00:35:11,499 --> 00:35:13,800
Oh, geez!

439
00:35:13,800 --> 00:35:18,499
He's supposed to be a man, but he
blacked out from just a couple drinks?

440
00:35:18,499 --> 00:35:20,700
How could you not remember what you did?

441
00:35:20,700 --> 00:35:22,999
Geez!
Geez!

442
00:35:30,600 --> 00:35:32,499
Oh no!

443
00:35:47,899 --> 00:35:50,200
