450
00:36:32,600 --> 00:36:35,800
What are you doing here?
Did you get hurt badly?

451
00:36:35,800 --> 00:36:37,499
- Quick! Get in!
- What? Why?

452
00:36:37,499 --> 00:36:39,499
- Hurry up!
- Why?

453
00:36:39,999 --> 00:36:42,200
- Geez.
- The door! Close the door!

454
00:36:42,200 --> 00:36:44,200
