460
00:37:26,300 --> 00:37:30,700
You're just my employer.

461
00:37:38,999 --> 00:37:41,899
Why are you being
so nice to her, Seo Woo?

462
00:37:48,200 --> 00:37:49,999
Oh, geez.

463
00:37:50,499 --> 00:37:52,300
Give me your hand.

464
00:37:52,800 --> 00:37:55,300
- Are you okay?
