486
00:39:53,200 --> 00:39:54,800
Are you hurt?

487
00:39:54,800 --> 00:39:57,100
A man's hips are the most
important part of a man's body!

488
00:39:57,100 --> 00:39:58,200
- Ow!
- Oh no!

489
00:39:58,200 --> 00:39:59,800
I'm fine.

490
00:40:00,399 --> 00:40:04,200
Um, Young Master. It's nice to see
