493
00:40:12,200 --> 00:40:13,899
Oh, really?

494
00:40:16,800 --> 00:40:19,300
Here, have this.

495
00:40:19,300 --> 00:40:21,399
Is he giving this to me
so that I get younger?

496
00:40:51,499 --> 00:40:53,800
